channel.title: 508 mismatched colors
channel.description:
There are some 'glitches' in the ip changer client involving colors such as the color of a blue party hat. To fix that go in your run.bat and change the game1 to game0.
Gotta give thanks to palidino76 for letting us know he's not really a haxor >.<
